{"tid":271604,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"評C朗vs美斯","createTime":"2017-06-05T08:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T06:24:50.000Z","uid":92886,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3292d59c2cc85d3dd07def7b124a1aad699770e9","tid":271604,"uid":92886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T08:31:12.000Z","msg":"近10年最強球員大多數球迷都會話佢兩個 客觀咁係幾個角度比較佢兩個：<br />\n<br />\n射術：美斯腳內側攞角度同埋單刀超純熟挑射真係好強；而c朗就勁在門前接應橫傳超敏銳觸覺搶點，而且射門腳頭比美斯重；各有各，呢項打和<br />\n<br />\n策劃派牌助攻：c朗主要做終結者既角色，入球機器，極少控球派牌，就算無睇開皇馬波，睇數據都可以知；美斯傳球能力，視野明顯較c朗出色，killer pass亦有，唔單止短傳，長傳都成熟，尤其右路斜斬去對方左邊禁區比左翼/閘入攝呢招都造過唔少入球；美斯勝<br />\n<br />\n盤球：曼聯時期c朗盤球出色但去左皇馬自己帶波做突破的確少左好多；美斯唔洗講，帶波帶到痴膠水，其入球周不時係過兩、三個防守球員先入；美斯勝<br />\n<br />\n身體質素：c朗身高同肌肉力量較美斯好，去到皇馬操得更大隻，造就c朗彈跳力驚人，頭磓完勝美斯；C朗勝<br />\n<br />\n心態：c朗唔服輸不斷迫自己進步/減慢自己衰老既精神好屈機，去到佢呢個位仲咁勤力訓練，比著其他好多球星已經偷懶，或者放鬆左，而比賽入面佢對勝利渴望既心態好多時對隊友有正面影響；而美斯國家隊多次決賽止步而退出國家隊單野比人感覺鬥心唔夠強；c朗勝<br />\n<br />\n其賽各有千秋，兩邊fans嘈乜姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c0b07f6eca769240b28af4646862cae537bc1b8","tid":271604,"uid":46035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T08:33:36.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"674050f505cbb3a63ac359a35ce2743e10105bf9","tid":271604,"uid":37747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T08:35:39.000Z","msg":"仲以為有咩新見解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來溫故炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7b73760ca0b7ff4958ec966428922d9846a137","tid":271604,"uid":97997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T08:35:54.000Z","msg":"C朗喺葡萄牙隊都有做美斯角色，喺中前場策動進攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各有春秋，比嚟做乜，然而美斯越踢越辛苦的確係事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d087353b1e4b18a9652d16abc007010f9ac224cc","tid":271604,"uid":18917,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T08:43:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5fb2fa9bb305d8cf45f7782893a2d22d2db7a02b","tid":271604,"uid":92886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T08:44:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>C朗喺葡萄牙隊都有做美斯角色，喺中前場策動進攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各有春秋，比嚟做乜，然而美斯越踢越辛苦的確係事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今季真係鄧佢慘，明明打翼，班中場廢jer到成日要佢落中場攞波"},{"pid":"793d817ad81e95f95f027416f5e4a73afec00f2b","tid":271604,"uid":25086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T08:46:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> C朗彈跳力真係好癲"},{"pid":"6cf0da9db7382c42bc9376f4cacba10ed8d6b25c","tid":271604,"uid":91875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T08:46:40.000Z","msg":"TOO LONG DIDNT READ<br />\n直接講邊個最勁"},{"pid":"ba6df602010cb9ed81973452ffd134aa0f6fa56a","tid":271604,"uid":42302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T08:48:18.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嘈乜姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唯恐天下不亂"},{"pid":"acd0d177fa3b9ce16cadd3a746e9b43bfb32046f","tid":271604,"uid":52123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T08:48:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>TOO LONG DIDNT READ<br />\n直接講邊個最勁</blockquote><br />\n美斯"},{"pid":"f3b7f29813aa66f1d01953c8dd05f27686efd97f","tid":271604,"uid":74009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T08:50:44.000Z","msg":"睇你點睇<br />\n射10球入4球<br />\n定<br />\n射5球入4球"},{"pid":"794125c2e3e2e3acf021e865f1020370cd2cefe2","tid":271604,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T08:56:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇你點睇<br />\n射10球入4球<br />\n定<br />\n射5球入4球</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你意思係牙朗射10球入4球?<br />\n<br />\n要比應該比食chance<br />\n<br />\n兩個基本都係有chance就食硬咁濟<br />\n<br />\n牙朗多左個5球射門係30碼鳩射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd91fcf76d09c69fad8b4b727a75d9194f6b57f","tid":271604,"uid":116896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T13:51:35.000Z","msg":"首先<br />\n賤種隊中前場屈，賤朗只需要等餵食殘廢餐<br />\n相反，美斯今季無左沙維小白，仍然係西甲神射手"},{"pid":"0cedb88c4b460aea258ba1825bf5e2a2380ce5db","tid":271604,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T13:56:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先<br />\n賤種隊中前場屈，賤朗只需要等餵食殘廢餐<br />\n相反，美斯今季無左沙維小白，仍然係西甲神射手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收檔啦<br />\n根本巴個戰術都係做比美斯後上既<br />\n蘇9尼馬都係開路, 兩個南美天王幫手仲想點<br />\n蘇9助攻仲多過美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d355dfa26bb56e3bfec8c879836558111b3e4831","tid":271604,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T14:00:00.000Z","msg":"其實阿朗傳波係唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭鎚二傳亦都勁<br />\n出波都好勁<br />\n左右開弓腳內外側腳面都出到波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e11b5b24ed09b959b362594f0519d12a04aa354","tid":271604,"uid":25231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T14:01:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先<br />\n賤種隊中前場屈，賤朗只需要等餵食殘廢餐<br />\n相反，美斯今季無左沙維小白，仍然係西甲神射手</blockquote><br />\n林生你係最熟悉美斯嘅人<br />\n你又話美斯唔care個人獎項<br />\n哩家又拎出黎j<br />\n你想點呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c63b1bf36bbb0fb5f049771d9d4a31de4691520","tid":271604,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T14:04:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>首先<br />\n賤種隊中前場屈，賤朗只需要等餵食殘廢餐<br />\n相反，美斯今季無左沙維小白，仍然係西甲神射手</blockquote><br />\n林生你係最熟悉美斯嘅人<br />\n你又話美斯唔care個人獎項<br />\n哩家又拎出黎j<br />\n你想點呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成日講到美斯退守中場呢樣個樣<br />\n